" Plugins
set surround

" Escape
imap · <Esc>
map · <Esc>

" Command mode
noremap <A-a> :

" Exit visual mode with 'v'
vnoremap v <Esc>

" Add punctuation to end of line
" Add punctuation to end of line
nmap <A-,> mqA,<Esc>`q
inoremap <A-,> <Esc>mqA,<Esc>`q
nmap <A-.> mqA;<Esc>`q
inoremap <A-.> <Esc>mqA;<Esc>`q
